{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"爱吃鱼的猫","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-02","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny69xhglibwTdtXsZThMzN9vBrsV5Za2s5icz3JnNer8Cn7miboICIlCEZnL6LVMbOYoNDxDibDlx4KT1nicenX0DE2Brh/0","content":"1.为什么要先打好地基再盖高楼；\n思维方式和地基一样是根基、是基础、是骨架，而具体知识是幕墙、是装饰、是血肉，能够更有整体性，更协调，也更丰满，有思想。其次，有了坚固的根基才能建立稳固的高楼，越高的大厦，需要的地基越坚固，因此，好的思维方式能够帮助我们更快更好更多的掌握具体知识。\n慢工出细活，工欲善其事必先利其器，我们应把更多的时间用在掌握思维方式上。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":2387,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1488414411000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Yanae Yang","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-01","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98WUxgnmxEpgcwKia4vSaVZr6Oyx2wYIgoMAk7cUOb6WN5T3vPfq7c4AdwgTmtGH75t6NspLErm5UhaZIYRRg6oTH/0","content":"题目：为什么要“先掌握思维方式再学习具体知识？”你能想到哪些类比问题？顺着类比问题思考，你又能得出哪些结论呢？\n\n磨刀不误砍柴工、工欲善其事必先利其器\n\n--〉节省很多时间、提高效率\n\n顺藤摸瓜\n\n--〉找到事物的主线，可以更有条理、有的放矢，而非一片散沙\n\n高屋建瓴\n\n--〉站在一定的高度，综观全局\n\n擒贼先擒王\n\n--〉抓住要害，其他的小喽罗就迎刃而解了\n\n结论：抓住主干、掌握方法，可以高效、透彻地学习知识。\n","voteCount":2,"commentCount":0,"submitId":2327,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1488355917000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"轻轻的菲","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-22","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEoibPTIXiabwRaYPAu409t7cxXcX1SyyoY3VC9Sj2zAEURtVAsnKu8fbVia26ic5K1h8PMtQ1bg1QdvA/0","content":"因为思维方式是一个人行为的根基和框架，思维方式是骨头，具体知识是肉，有股有肉的丰满形象是最受欢迎的。但是一个人的骨架是比较难以改变，肉却可以随时减肥或者增肥来达到目的，相对来说比较容易获得。所以，思维方式是底层，知识是填充。\n其次，思维方式和具体知识就像是改造房子的地基和建筑材料。只有地基打稳了，房子的材料才能更好地发挥威力。\n","voteCount":3,"commentCount":2,"submitId":1542,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487763212000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Yovena","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-22","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6945c0LHicJ3JvRm1ZibQia86sXFSYshuhXpCicG8nagS0j1HfkHPv1pVG4ChI6oTIDqib9X8tf6KiaWGvIW07tTenEKE/0","content":"修房子为什么要先搭好内部骨架，再进行外部装修？这样结构更稳固，外加装饰时更安全","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":1514,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487755489000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"门前两只猫\uD83D\uDC08","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-22","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98WMqrFZYyRU8SGKLMX2aynur3FBOZrC5EQ90ibyWLrBy9jPtBrKBwYtZDgIicnkKqnMBBUCCKoC3bIBuZgjp0fahic/0","content":"思维方式是学习的基础，有好的思维学习知识才能学的又好又快，所以思维是根基，知识只是枝节，我们不能本末倒置。\n比如:为什么建造一栋房子总是要先打好地基，再去添加砖瓦？\n我觉得唯有打好思维这个地基，掌握科学的方法，学东西才会越学越好，知识也才会掌握的越来越牢固。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":1455,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487731821000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"珊珊","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6YKbBOXsVPz5kiaBYPPobsyEB0jacWoC1oz2A6ia8M7gmxtJiaribC7O7uHsleia2qcBuzJph3K5IxuxVA/0","content":"读书先了解框架，再开始阅读。从整体到局部，理解会更深刻","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":1272,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487625634000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"为什么要先了解规则再进行比赛？掌握了方法才能更好地实践。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":1004,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487491611000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"施伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEo9P2jC2S2gtzmiaPWycP2Fd6c8Lvunc8sP0iapaIrzxCur3tMr7Bia6kYfGXE4Pn3CLxmAUW8nr6ZK/0","content":"新设备要看说明书，在操作。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":859,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487383602000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"贾丹","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEmZHxxW6RutcFwjIMf9uz1r69ibLNmx5GBrgfLaIQKvkz0pVgu9Zlt7LqNBk6DLOrcEwVYxicVQhCj/0","content":"它可以帮助我们充分开拓自己的思路，创造性地解决问题。查找工作问题和小河流水：按流程走，一步一步，从源头出发","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":848,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487380575000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqUiaGZPHI2ga7E0gShutjcib8GKdDjQktSAdYIKa4icV4VOImzSz7BGe9nzia5iaxFMrTH0qEmSRDnhN/0","content":"先会走再会跑\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":809,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487320173000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"石榴","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ajG0rVIcxQPhYqEtzJ4QF0LFEUmBCh240Ou1S9ItxzPSmyYqibwuEpFYRUicLyKeVeBqg6AtfHa9iaJlOwlQicrXpO/0","content":"1、先感悟艺术再进行设计\n2、先学内功心法再习武学招式\n\n以道御招","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":745,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487165818000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jia ","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEmolDQEsp19ESuZXtIbYwHjiabZPCLcfCbI7X5SEP8FuxMRhN8gDLYphxpiaQ9KAWGwJjZ47oobqGJ/0","content":"类比问题：\n\nQ: 为什么“磨刀不误砍柴工”？\nA：只有有了更好的工具，做了充足的准备，才能在真正砍柴的时候又快又省力\n\nQ：为什么“授人以鱼不如授人以渔”？\nA：物质（鱼）是很快会消耗（吃）掉，只有掌握了方法（抓鱼），才能确保今后也能有想要的物质（鱼）。","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":701,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487041767000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张俊_Jun","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-08","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoI5t7uoDHPleojz3B7SWcfpqpus6sS2nlJ6ODic9X9gibTYy22MEW2DTuhmU3turZcm9VhkPStHlicG/0","content":"先掌握思维框架，在分析解决问题。\n先着手方法论学习，在开展工作。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":532,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486515845000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"慕容依","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEKib0YjdFPpaJa7Hqat2Ug4a50kNcl5eqgcqTpwYCZcgxIV32qK9T7Tg99uDx5bvVoZIE1PgggJm6g/0","content":"为什么“要先学会搭配衣服再去买衣服”？\n\n\n一切问题都要看对象，看前提，看背景。这是圈儿教我们的吧。\n对于题目中的这个问题，细想来，其实应该是有个隐含前提的，对于我们这些已经正在接受或者已经接受过高等教育的成年人来说，为什么要先掌握思维方式再学习具体知识？如果是对小孩子来说，明明就是学知识先。回顾我们从小到大的学习历程，学习就是从点滴知识的积累开始的，是通过对更多更广泛的知识的学习，才派生了对思维方式学习的需求。具体知识和思维方式的关系不完全是高下之分，更像是血肉同胞，你中有我，我中有你。站在知识之山的高度上，突然觉得思维方式好高端好需要啊，但是不要忘了，不踩着脚下的石头一节节上来，你还真就没有思维方式之烦恼！\n\n类比的买衣服问题也是这个道理。学会搭配衣服自然是很高端的做法，但这也是建立在买了一些衣服的基础上，大家都能看见那些有钱的大明星也土过，他们的时尚进阶之路也是摸爬滚打。在买中学搭配，在搭配中学会精明的买。\n\n\n这是一个很好的问题。","voteCount":2,"commentCount":0,"submitId":502,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486379618000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Pan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5KhpQIRIpY7DYXTlcKMicsq47nNJOC9PJu3VFIvUZUn410lK377dOFpG8rWiaoJQia6vpIP3zyVuEV/0","content":"1 先磨刀还是直接砍柴？--先磨刀","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":471,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486214741000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"怪盗KID",